Veteran actor, Mike Mvelase, fondly known as 'Khaphela' has been hogging headlines reporting that he might spend "Christmas on the Streets" due to the bank allegedly repossessed his home before putting it up for auction. These 4 stars had it all at some point. Great careers, big houses in nice suburbs but somehow they ended up homeless. Some of the have managed to rise back up and some haven't. 1. Mike Mvelase  2. Pamela Nomvete  3. Sechaba Pali  4. Tinah Mnumzana  5. Philemon Masinga 